WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.000
HOOK: Imagine you're a bee, embarking on a journey to a radiant sunflower. Each day, a new adventure awaits.

2
00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:06.000
BODY: You collect nectar, the sweet reward for your diligence. With care, you contribute to the hive, each effort a significant piece of a grander whole.

3
00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:09.000
CTA: Be like the bee. Embrace your journey, no matter how small your actions may seem. Every effort counts towards your goal. Spread your wings, and fly towards your sunflower today.
